reviewText: As with all the instructional sets made by Stephan Kesting (Grapplearts) this one was very well organized, clearly taught, and full of a mix of both fundamental and new techniques.  Great set!

I have Brandon Mullins' previous DVD instruction and I loved it.  This second one is even better.  Wow!  Super effective techniques taught in an organized logical flow.  Mullins is an exceptional instructor.  One of the best I've ever seen.

This is an instructional set on the highest level available.
An integration of high percentage sweeps, submissions and guard passes that will make
you a better fighter.

Pshemek Drabczynski
I love it! It meets the standard that I expect from Brandon and Stephan
As the title describes, these DVDs are non-stop Jiu-Jitsu.  Back to back, for hours on end.  Clear instructions, quality audio and video.
